Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.56,0:00:02.00,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After spending Tanabata in a state of melancholy...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.66,0:00:10.15,HaruhiCaption,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}[Tanabata: festival celebrating the meeting of stars Altair and Vega on July 7th]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.00,0:00:08.06,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...Haruhi made a full recovery from her blues during term exams...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.06,0:00:10.85,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and went back to doing whatever she wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.15,0:00:15.91,HaruhiSignSerif,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\bord0.01\fs16\frx20\frz1\pos(599,75)}Japanese
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.15,0:00:15.91,HaruhiSignSerif,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\bord0.01\fs16\frx20\frz1\pos(598,228)}Answer Sheet
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.85,0:00:12.29,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.29,0:00:15.70,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I felt like the blue baton of melancholy had been passed to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.70,0:00:17.21,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Totally down in the dumps.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.19,0:00:21.01,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And Haruhi, taking her test in the seat behind me...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.01,0:00:23.46,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...somehow always had time to spare...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.46,0:00:27.42,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and could usually be found sleeping on her desk thirty minutes before time was up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.42,0:00:28.49,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.49,0:00:29.45,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, so annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.45,0:00:30.25,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.94,0:02:03.37,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As far as Haruhi is concerned...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.37,0:02:06.37,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...the SOS Brigade apparently never takes a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.47,0:02:08.48,HaruhiTitleOverlay,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fs32\fad(490,490)\pos(352,47)}Mystérique Sign
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.37,0:02:09.85,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even during exam season when club activities were suspended...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.85,0:02:12.29,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...this enigma of a brigade which wasn't even a club or anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.29,0:02:13.98,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...much like a convenience store...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.98,0:02:15.89,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...met year-round without a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.63,0:02:17.47,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.47,0:02:18.47,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.12,0:02:24.95,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.95,0:02:26.53,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.53,0:02:27.69,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.69,0:02:28.96,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.96,0:02:31.63,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my SOS Brigade emblem!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.63,0:02:33.05,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Emblem?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.05,0:02:36.76,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like a grumbling, drunken tapeworm to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.76,0:02:38.13,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Look closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.13,0:02:38.91,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,See.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.91,0:02:41.87,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It says SOS Brigade in the center, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.34,0:02:44.72,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When you put it that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.72,0:02:47.16,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...I can't say that I don't get the feeling it doesn't or does it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.16,0:02:50.30,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But you can't say that it wouldn't be difficult to assert that claim.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.30,0:02:50.82,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.82,0:02:53.45,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How many negatives did I just string together?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.45,0:02:55.32,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If someone's free, tally it up for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.32,0:02:57.37,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one with the most free time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.72,0:03:02.43,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'm thinking about putting this on the SOS Brigade's top page.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.43,0:03:05.04,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}On that pathetic site that only has a top page?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.04,0:03:08.42,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The site you made won't bring in visitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.42,0:03:09.89,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You should feel mortified.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.89,0:03:12.27,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We totally don't have anything to liven it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.27,0:03:14.10,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because you got in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.10,0:03:17.71,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And I was planning on attracting visitors with erotic images of Mikuru-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.05,0:03:19.52,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I came up with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.52,0:03:22.80,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,How about putting up something like an SOS Brigade symbol?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.17,0:03:26.96,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just delete this retarded homepage off the Internet already.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.96,0:03:29.55,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The access counter hasn't even reached three digits...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.55,0:03:32.85,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and ninety percent of those hits were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.23,0:03:35.39,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you write a journal?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.39,0:03:37.78,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it the chief's job to put up a task schedule?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.78,0:03:39.55,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Screw that. It's a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.55,0:03:40.90,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It'd be a pain for me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.59,0:03:43.87,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Kyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.87,0:03:47.70,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Make this symbol display at the top of the site.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.70,0:03:49.22,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You do it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.22,0:03:50.93,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the brigade chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.93,0:03:53.12,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The chief's job is to give orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.12,0:03:54.97,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, if I do everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.97,0:03:57.61,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...you guys won't have any work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.61,0:04:00.12,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You should try to use your head every once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.12,0:04:03.15,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't become a better person if you just do as you're told.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.52,0:04:05.42,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you telling me to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.42,0:04:06.67,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Or not to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.67,0:04:07.69,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Which is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.69,0:04:09.42,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Just do it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.65,0:04:13.03,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I reluctantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.03,0:04:15.78,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...took master artist Haruhi-sama's portrait of a tapeworm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.78,0:04:17.87,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...did some half-assed resizing...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.87,0:04:19.99,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...pasted it onto the file and uploaded it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.67,0:04:23.89,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Starting tomorrow, I get a brief break...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.89,0:04:26.32,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...a testing vacation, which lasts until summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.32,0:04:29.98,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It would be the period when teachers mark my test answers wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.98,0:04:31.58,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damn, this is annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:34.79,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At least I can go ogle Asahina-san for some peace of mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.43,0:04:39.25,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Expecting to hear a "Yes?" in Asahina-san's voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.25,0:04:40.40,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...I knocked on the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.40,0:04:41.38,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.59,0:04:45.33,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. It's just you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.33,0:04:46.44,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki's also here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.25,0:04:50.78,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's like an accessory for this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.78,0:04:52.67,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You don't have to include her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.67,0:04:54.39,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Officially, she's a member of the Literary Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.39,0:04:56.41,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I should still correct myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.87,0:04:58.83,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. It's just you and Nagato.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.33,0:05:01.67,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a complaint about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.67,0:05:04.57,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I were to list out my complaints concerning you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.57,0:05:07.92,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...I would end up completely covering both sides of an A4 sheet of paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.29,0:05:09.72,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Knocking on the door...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.72,0:05:12.40,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...makes me think that a visitor must have come to see us, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.40,0:05:16.72,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm taking care so that I don't witness a live Asahina-san clothes changing session.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.27,0:05:19.05,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That careless, charming person...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.05,0:05:21.82,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...can't seem to remember to lock the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.22,0:05:24.09,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by visitor?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.09,0:05:26.18,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.18,0:05:29.83,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's not going to start talking about what happened on Tanabata three years ago, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.83,0:05:31.60,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.60,0:05:33.49,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Without obtaining my permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.85,0:05:35.24,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What might you be talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.24,0:05:37.32,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That poster you put up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.65,0:05:39.24,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.22,0:05:41.82,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Actually, a while back...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.82,0:05:43.68,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...I appealed to the student council...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.68,0:05:47.04,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...to allow the SOS Brigade to exist as a counseling group.
