Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.79,0:05:49.40,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I even put up a poster...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.40,0:05:51.51,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and threw it up on a bulletin board I happened to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.11,0:05:53.05,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.05,0:05:54.05,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.05,0:05:55.02,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.70,0:05:57.88,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe the computer's acting up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.10,0:06:00.99,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The SOS Brigade emblem...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.99,0:06:03.30,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...appeared distorted as though it had been gathered.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.30,0:06:05.76,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And the counter and title logo were plain gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:08.16,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It looked subtly different from the one I made.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.47,0:06:14.13,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the file on the server is corrupt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.13,0:06:15.67,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,How long has it been like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.67,0:06:16.56,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.56,0:06:18.32,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It was like this when I checked today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.32,0:06:20.13,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Who should I complain to?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.13,0:06:22.09,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to go complain.
