Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.53,0:06:30.81,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.81,0:06:31.53,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.53,0:06:34.01,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Those hackers or crackers people talk about!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.01,0:06:35.12,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.12,0:06:36.43,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably some kind of error.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.43,0:06:37.92,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.92,0:06:41.49,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe someone's committing cyber-terrorism against the SOS Brigade!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.49,0:06:42.76,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.76,0:06:47.23,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If I find that person, I'll skip the trial and sentence him to thirty days of community service!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.40,0:06:49.24,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.22,0:06:51.45,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Now this is rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.89,0:06:54.00,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Asahina-san has yet to show up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.00,0:06:56.54,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Second years have extra testing, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.78,0:06:59.03,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We could have gone home already...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.03,0:07:02.20,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...so why are we all gathered here?
