Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.35,0:07:13.93,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I really can't wait for Asahina-san's tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.64,0:07:17.56,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.91,0:07:18.79,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Wrong! Wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.22,0:07:20.23,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I spent the subsequent period of time...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.79,0:07:19.37,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.37,0:07:20.39,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}There! Left!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.23,0:07:23.48,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...complying with Haruhi's unreasonable demands.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.39,0:07:21.21,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.48,0:07:24.38,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.13,0:07:27.90,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That was the sound of salvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.49,0:07:26.65,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.51,0:07:31.37,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.37,0:07:33.65,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I had tests until fourth period.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.65,0:07:36.25,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The person who just appeared while humbly apologizing...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.25,0:07:37.95,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...would be our clubroom's exclusive angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.95,0:07:39.50,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Asahina-san has descended.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.14,0:07:43.14,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Well... That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.03,0:07:46.16,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.16,0:07:48.20,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought a visitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.82,0:07:55.54,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How can this be!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.54,0:07:59.11,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nobody was ever supposed to come seeking counseling yet here's our first one!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.37,0:08:01.47,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Her name was Emiri Kimidori-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.47,0:08:04.07,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A second year who appeared soft-spoken and well-groomed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.07,0:08:09.07,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So you want our SOS Brigade to look for your missing boyfriend, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.18,0:08:10.95,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.38,0:08:15.55,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Apparently...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.55,0:08:18.39,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...she actually thinks the purpose of this club is to...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.39,0:08:20.11,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...offer counsel...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.11,0:08:22.57,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...or perform odd jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.00,0:08:25.09,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So what might be troubling you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.08,0:08:29.51,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,He hasn't come to school for many days now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.51,0:08:31.00,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you try calling him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.00,0:08:33.81,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't answer his cell or his home phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.81,0:08:36.41,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I went to his home, but he wasn't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.81,0:08:39.97,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What about your boyfriend's family?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.97,0:08:42.25,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,He lives by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.25,0:08:45.58,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard that his parents live overseas.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.95,0:08:48.47,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't know how to contact them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.96,0:08:50.54,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Would they happen to be in Canada?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.54,0:08:51.29,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.29,0:08:53.65,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe it was Honduras.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.16,0:08:55.34,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Honduras, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.34,0:08:56.38,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.38,0:08:58.10,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"I see," my ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.10,0:09:00.68,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I doubt you even know where it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.68,0:09:01.72,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.72,0:09:03.72,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Was it somewhere below Mexico?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.72,0:09:06.40,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,His room was completely dark when I went at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.40,0:09:07.95,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.94,0:09:11.28,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I can understand how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:12.24,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Like hell you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.24,0:09:14.10,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You can't possibly understand how it feels to be in love!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.10,0:09:14.92,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.92,0:09:17.23,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm amazed you came to our SOS Brigade.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.23,0:09:18.55,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What was the cause?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.55,0:09:22.76,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,He mentioned the SOS Brigade numerous times.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.42,0:09:24.99,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's your boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.84,0:09:27.16,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.07,0:09:28.95,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,—.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.54,0:09:30.78,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.31,0:09:35.81,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe he said that he was neighbors with the SOS Brigade.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.43,0:09:41.46,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,He serves as the president of the Computer Research Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.42,0:09:47.38,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The one Haruhi took pictures of sexually harassing Asahina-san!
