Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.23,0:12:35.95,HaruhiCaption,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\be1\shad0\bord2\3a&H00&\fry30\1c&H6F5530&\3c&H6B615C&\move(73,224,-23,224)}Calculator Man
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.47,0:12:33.66,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he on a trip to Central and South America?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.66,0:12:35.70,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Or are his whereabouts really hidden?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.23,0:12:37.37,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be best if we left.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.83,0:12:40.33,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I think this is the first I've heard her speak today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.33,0:12:41.45,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.45,0:12:42.64,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't use a serious tone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.64,0:12:43.64,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't breathe on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.64,0:12:44.46,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your face is really close.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.46,0:12:45.32,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Freaking me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.09,0:12:47.97,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel strangely out of place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.32,0:12:51.80,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I am familiar with a similar sensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.58,0:12:51.80,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H000000&}- Found warabimochi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.68,0:12:55.88,HaruhiCaption,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}[Warabimochi: summer confection of bracken starch and sweet toasted soybean flour]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.15,0:12:54.37,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It expired three days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.37,0:12:55.88,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat it so it doesn't go to waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.57,0:12:59.35,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Mikuru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.20,0:12:59.26,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H000000&}- No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.22,0:13:03.43,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What similar sensation?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.94,0:13:05.34,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Closed space.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.34,0:13:08.24,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This room smells the same as that place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.24,0:13:11.10,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right. You're an actual esper.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.10,0:13:12.80,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A dimensional rift exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.80,0:13:14.90,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Phase conversion is occurring.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.79,0:13:18.97,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Looks like we should pull out immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.33,0:13:25.78,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.78,0:13:27.66,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's dismissed for the day!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.66,0:13:28.40,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.40,0:13:29.38,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What about solving the case?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.73,0:13:31.28,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll work itself out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.76,0:13:32.46,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.19,0:13:34.77,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It seems like she's already bored with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.75,0:13:40.22,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Um.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.74,0:13:42.13,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.13,0:13:45.45,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you tell us to reassemble without Suzumiya-san noticing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.45,0:13:46.71,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Those two...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.71,0:13:48.96,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...are concerned about the room we were just in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.96,0:13:49.89,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.89,0:13:50.53,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.89,0:13:54.27,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We should learn more once we go back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.27,0:13:55.73,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Nagato-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.83,0:14:03.12,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A limited-area amalgamated alternate timespace with non-corrosive tendencies...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.12,0:14:05.46,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...is independently occurring in restricted mode within this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.46,0:14:09.92,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's hard when you sound like you just randomly picked out words from a dictionary.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.92,0:14:13.42,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The sensation I'm experiencing is similar to that of closed space.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.42,0:14:15.56,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That space originates from Suzumiya-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.56,0:14:17.68,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...but this gives off a different scent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.06,0:14:19.08,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagato-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.08,0:14:22.28,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the president's disappearance a result of this abnormal space?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.28,0:14:23.20,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.79,0:14:29.28,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I should have told her to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.47,0:14:36.14,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I had no time to enjoy the sensation against my arm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.14,0:14:38.62,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was desperately trying to verify my current location.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.62,0:14:41.67,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure I was in that cramped studio apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.67,0:14:43.59,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Not an eerie place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.59,0:14:45.35,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Entry code analyzed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.35,0:14:47.14,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This place overlaps normal space.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.14,0:14:48.76,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A phase has merely slipped off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.76,0:14:51.00,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't appear to be closed space.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.00,0:14:52.37,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It is deceptively similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.37,0:14:58.26,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,However, a sector of this dataspace contains traces of junk data originating from Haruhi Suzumiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.26,0:14:59.48,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,How significant are these traces?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.48,0:15:01.19,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Of an inconsequent level.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.19,0:15:03.15,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She was merely the trigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.15,0:15:04.39,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.39,0:15:05.62,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.62,0:15:07.65,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are Asahina-san and I not part of this conversation!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.95,0:15:11.24,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the Computer Society president here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.55,0:15:12.86,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It would seem so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.86,0:15:15.39,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This alternate space appeared in his room...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.39,0:15:17.92,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...and trapped him within for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.33,0:15:19.71,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.33,0:15:22.17,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.67,0:15:25.42,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you tell me what you're doing first?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.42,0:15:27.38,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like a moment to prepare myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.70,0:15:28.38,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.20,0:15:31.09,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.09,0:15:31.47,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.06,0:15:33.34,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.34,0:15:35.84,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I can sense a clear intent of animosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.43,0:15:39.25,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They might have the means to defend themselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.25,0:15:41.32,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...but Asahina-san and I can't feel so secure!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.33,0:15:44.76,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have like a beam gun or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.78,0:15:47.73,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's prohibited to carry a weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.73,0:15:48.57,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.88,0:15:50.28,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.28,0:15:52.85,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not only is it likely that this person would still be useless even with a weapon...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.85,0:15:55.64,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...she seems prone to accidentally leave it on the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.30,0:16:03.04,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you aware of an insect known as the cave cricket?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.04,0:16:06.00,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you aren't, I'd like to show you what I'm seeing right this moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.86,0:16:07.79,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.17,0:16:09.13,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A cave cricket, I presume.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.39,0:16:10.07,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That much I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.07,0:16:10.88,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not asking about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.88,0:16:12.84,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The Creator of this space.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.84,0:16:14.80,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be Haruhi's doing again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.80,0:16:16.13,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The origin lies elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.13,0:16:17.69,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But she started it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.62,0:16:20.22,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You can move now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.99,0:16:25.61,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,While imperfect...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.61,0:16:28.17,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...my power appears to be effective here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.97,0:16:31.44,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,My strength is one tenth of what it is in closed space.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.44,0:16:33.78,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps it was judged that this much would suffice?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.05,0:16:36.49,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, Nagato.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.49,0:16:38.14,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the true identity of that bug?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.14,0:16:39.59,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the president?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.59,0:16:41.66,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A subspecies of data life form.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.66,0:16:43.91,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It is using the brain tissue of a male student...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.91,0:16:46.37,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...to heighten its probability for existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.37,0:16:48.79,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that the president is inside this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.79,0:16:49.83,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.83,0:16:50.99,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.99,0:16:54.99,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This cave cricket is the president's visualization of an object of fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.99,0:16:57.53,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If we defeat it, this alternate space will collapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.96,0:16:58.87,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.87,0:17:00.10,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You are not.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.10,0:17:02.20,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, it's quite simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.00,0:17:05.99,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Due to Asahina-san engaging me in lower-body exercises...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.99,0:17:07.65,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...I'm about to lose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.65,0:17:09.66,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And she's taken away my ability to move so I can't escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.10,0:17:11.33,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't take long.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.81,0:17:14.15,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Get it over with.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.45,0:17:15.72,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.67,0:17:18.83,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Fumoffu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.39,0:17:31.05,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Repulsion field!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.39,0:17:42.40,HaruhiCaption,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs30\shad0\bord2\3a&H00&\pos(352,432)}Scarab {\c&H3734D0&}healed {\1c&HFFFFFF&}your wounds !
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.78,0:17:46.90,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Second Raid!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.28,0:17:51.12,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.60,0:17:55.83,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.04,0:18:08.09,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it over?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.79,0:18:14.85,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Looks like he's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.16,0:18:18.01,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And we returned to the cramped studio apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.36,0:18:25.45,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Approximately two hundred eight million years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.45,0:18:27.55,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,After landing on Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.55,0:18:31.08,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...it discovered that it lacked the means to exist on Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.08,0:18:33.45,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...so it went into hibernation to allow self-preservation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.06,0:18:37.20,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Once humans gave birth to computer networks...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.20,0:18:38.88,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...it reached a half-awakened state.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.04,0:18:42.11,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, data of an amount incomputable using common numbers...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.11,0:18:44.51,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...transmitted from a parallel world caused it to awaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.84,0:18:46.49,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Data from a parallel world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.49,0:18:50.28,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That was the SOS Brigade emblem Haruhi drew.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.28,0:18:51.94,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That was evidently the trigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.94,0:18:54.89,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,When this crest is converted to a terrestrial standard...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.89,0:18:58.02,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...it holds approximately four hundred thirty-six petabytes of data.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.02,0:18:59.09,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.09,0:19:00.80,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't even a hundred kilobytes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.80,0:19:04.23,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A symbol she just happened to draw ended up being such an incredible thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.23,0:19:06.41,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She truly is Suzumiya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.15,0:19:09.38,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was seriously scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.23,0:19:11.33,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It went too well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.25,0:19:14.16,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The formation of the SOS Brigade...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.16,0:19:16.71,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Just because Asahina-san was perfectly suited to being a club mascot...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.71,0:19:18.51,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...and because Koizumi transferred in...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.51,0:19:21.41,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...and because Nagato was there from the start, they became members.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.41,0:19:22.37,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And as it turns out...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.37,0:19:24.31,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...Asahina-san is actually a time-traveler...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.31,0:19:25.98,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...and Nagato a pseudo-alien.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.98,0:19:28.06,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If all of this came from Haruhi's mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.06,0:19:30.04,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...it would just fit too perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.98,0:19:34.09,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Koizumi would tell me it's because Haruhi desired it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.09,0:19:36.23,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...but I don't believe that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.23,0:19:38.09,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm just an ordinary person myself, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.44,0:19:39.21,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.21,0:19:42.48,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...what if there were another side to all of Haruhi's actions?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.73,0:19:48.63,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What if I have some unusual power myself like the three of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.63,0:19:49.90,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...or some kind of ability...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.90,0:19:52.96,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and Haruhi made me an SOS Brigade member for that reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.98,0:19:58.21,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Who am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.78,0:19:59.95,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Simply put...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.27,0:20:02.78,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I am the SOS Brigade's only conscience.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.09,0:20:05.62,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Making Haruhi stop her unlawful club activities...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.62,0:20:07.96,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...to allow us to live out a normal high school life...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.96,0:20:09.64,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...is the reason I am here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.94,0:20:12.35,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So in the end, what exactly was that cave cricket?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.35,0:20:13.69,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A data life form.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.08,0:20:15.65,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A relative of your patron?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.65,0:20:17.13,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Their origin was the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.13,0:20:18.82,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,However, these undertook a different path of evolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.82,0:20:19.86,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And met destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.49,0:20:21.98,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or so they thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.98,0:20:24.04,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But a survivor was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.04,0:20:26.66,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It didn't have to hibernate on Earth of all places.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.66,0:20:29.06,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It could have gone to sleep somewhere around Neptune.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.06,0:20:30.79,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To think that the development of the Internet...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.79,0:20:32.87,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...would be the breeding grounds for a mimicry of an evil god.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.23,0:20:35.56,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.00,0:20:38.96,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,When Haruhi brought up the picture here...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.96,0:20:40.55,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...and when she first completed the picture...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.55,0:20:41.97,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...nothing happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.38,0:20:45.61,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Because this room had already been transformed into alternate space.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.61,0:20:48.72,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A variety of types of elements and force fields battled one another...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.72,0:20:51.32,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...and negated one another, creating a state of saturation...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.34,0:20:53.44,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...which means there is no further room for assimilation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.44,0:20:55.36,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So while I wasn't paying attention...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.36,0:20:57.41,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...the clubroom was turned into a den of evil, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.78,0:20:59.77,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe it to be harmless.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.77,0:21:00.41,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Most likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.70,0:21:02.18,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.18,0:21:04.57,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I can live without sudden changes in behavior...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.57,0:21:07.04,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...or any urges to go looking for a hanging rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.40,0:21:09.38,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm working hard to prevent that from happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.80,0:21:13.17,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure this isn't happening because you're working hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.22,0:21:19.22,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The access counter had climbed to almost thirty thousand!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.22,0:21:21.37,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This data life form...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.37,0:21:24.11,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...placed hyperlinks in various locations to multiply.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.11,0:21:25.99,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It copied its own data into...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.99,0:21:27.56,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...the brains of humans who saw the sign...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.56,0:21:29.94,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...which in turn created restricted space.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.96,0:21:32.62,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, since the data was damaged...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.62,0:21:36.65,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...people who saw the sign did not necessarily end up like the president.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.48,0:21:38.82,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}From what Nagato said...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.82,0:21:41.04,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...only eight idiots saw the correct image.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.04,0:21:42.86,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And five of those were students in North High.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.86,0:21:44.87,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We probably need to go save them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.87,0:21:46.13,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, ladies!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.13,0:21:47.58,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Get your asses over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.17,0:21:50.20,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you strain your eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.20,0:21:52.17,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...you'll see that it actually says ZOZ Brigade.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.71,0:21:54.79,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nagato did a retake on the symbol...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.79,0:21:56.01,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and I pasted it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.32,0:21:57.97,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The president came to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.04,0:21:59.63,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.03,0:22:03.25,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So it was just freshman blues or a lovers' quarrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.25,0:22:04.99,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, isn't it amazing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.99,0:22:07.10,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Our access counter hit thirty thousand!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.10,0:22:09.52,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess visitors keep coming back for more.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.91,0:22:11.99,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Could it be that...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.42,0:22:16.42,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...she was the one who destroyed the data?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.73,0:22:19.35,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And the person who brought this matter to our attention, Kimidori-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.35,0:22:21.70,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Upon asking the president, he apparently doesn't have a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.61,0:22:25.20,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nagato was always at the center...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.20,0:22:26.75,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...of this perfectly scripted scenario.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.75,0:22:28.76,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If this all-purpose alien terminal...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.76,0:22:30.73,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...had done something to Kimidori-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.73,0:22:32.84,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...so she would bring us the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.84,0:22:34.38,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...I wouldn't be surprised at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.38,0:22:35.75,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She could have set up the pretend client...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.75,0:22:39.38,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...in an attempt to ease away some of Haruhi's boredom.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.94,0:22:42.18,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It couldn't be that for all this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.18,0:22:45.75,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...she's been preventing weird incidents before they happen without saying a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.75,0:22:47.31,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In silence, from the shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.35,0:22:52.52,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or did you bring us in, Nagato...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.52,0:22:54.46,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...because you wished for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.46,0:22:58.63,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As an alien-made android living for years in a totally empty room...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.35,0:23:00.25,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nagato...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.63,0:23:03.88,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Perhaps you also feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.89,0:23:07.29,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...lonely when you're alone.
